<p class="artwork">Frontispiece: Portrait of Thomas Hardy</p>
<p class="artist">Henry Macbeth-Raeburn</p>
<p class="artdate">1895</p>
<p class="medium">Etching</p>
<p class="size">11 x 8.7 cm</p>
<p class="place">Facing title-page in Hardy's <span class="book">Tess of the 
D'Urbervilles</span>.</p>
<p class="comment">Volume 1 of the First Uniform Edition of the Wessex Novels, with 
illustrations by Henry Macbeth-Raeburn. London: Osgood-McIlvaine, 1895.</p>
		
<li><a href="3b.jpg">Title-page</a></li>
<li><a href="3c.jpg">Hardy's signature (facing frontispiece)</a></li>
	
